				p.lead
					| Currently in 5th Semester of Software Engineering- Interactive Gaming. I have a Bachelor of Science in Biology at Ryerson University.
			.col-md-5.col-md-pull-7
				img.featurette-image.img-responsive.center-block(src='../Assets/images/Sunflower (Mature).JPG', alt='Biology Lab', style="width:700px;height:500px" )
