		.row.featurette
			.col-md-7
				h2.featurette-heading
					| My Hobbies:
					span.text-muted  Games!! PCMR!!
				p.lead
					| I play all kinds of games and they vary from mobile to PC. The game I play the most is on mobile called Soccer Spirits. Other games I play are League Of Legends, Diablo 3, Overwatch, Undertale.
