					| Other than staying at home all day playing games, I love to go camping. I been to Algonquin Park (Lake of Two Rivers, Pog Lake), Emily Provincial Park, and Earl Rowe
			.col-md-5.col-md-pull-7
				img.featurette-image.img-responsive.center-block(src="Assets/images/Camp-Fire.jpg" alt="Camp-Fire" style="width:500px;height:500px;")
